                            gifts, CC coins, even Bolts spends all chip away at their HP. Last to land the
                            killing blow takes the crown.
                        </TextBlock>

                        <Border Style="{StaticResource Card}" Margin="0 0 0 14">
                            <StackPanel>
                                <TextBlock Text="Pool" Style="{StaticResource H2}" />
